snippet.title: OUTLANDER Final Season Official Trailer (2026)
snippet.description:
Official Outlander Season 8 Series Trailer 2026 | More ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/App | Caitríona Balfe Series Trailer | STARZ: 6 Mar 2026 | Details ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/show/kgj/outlander-2014?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=description
The story of Claire Randall, a married combat nurse from 1945 who is mysteriously swept back in time to 1743, where she is immediately thrown into an unknown world where her life is threatened. When she is forced to marry Jamie, a chivalrous and romantic young Scottish warrior, a passionate affair is ignited that tears Claire's heart between two vastly different men in two irreconcilable lives.

Outlander (2026) is the new drama series by Jamie Payne, Mairzee Almas, Mike Barker, John Dahl, Jennifer Getzinger, Denise Di Novi, Annie Griffin, Stephen Woolfenden, Douglas Mackinnon, Anna Foerster, Justin Molotnikov, Brian Kelly, Julian Holmes, David Moore, Metin Hüseyin & Charlotte Brändström, starring Caitríona Balfe, Sam Heughan and Richard Rankin.
